headline: BD Launches Industry-First Bioabsorbable Mesh Designed for Umbilical Hernia Repair
summary: BD (Becton, Dickinson and Company) (NYSE: BDX), a leading global medical technology company, today announced 510(k) clearance from the U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) and the commercial launch of Phasix™ ST Umbilical Hernia Patch, the first and only fully absorbable hernia patch on the market designed specifically for umbilical hernias.
